{"tid":204233,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Dark Souls 黑暗靈魂系列[4] The Ringed City 環印城 DLC","createTime":"2017-04-17T00:38:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T10:58:10.000Z","uid":18104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7b5ed3b580f14ad5b5464209a661466c4b99e71b","tid":204233,"uid":18104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T00:38:17.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/29w7p1yq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F29w7p1yq&h=0fc3ecc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSteam:<br />\n<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/374320/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F374320%2F&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=2fdb4725\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/374320/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/506971/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F506971%2F&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=e111ed99\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/506971/</a><br />\n買Season Pass=連所有DLC<br />\nDeluxe Edition=Game連DLC<br />\n<br />\n<strong>DARK SOULS III THE FIRE FADES EDITION</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/trpsoyf1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftrpsoyf1&h=95eb5ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4月20日先推出<br />\n主機版GAME連DLC<br />\n<br />\nDLC2入口:初始火爐/DLC1修女營火<br />\n展示人性既牆:係湖到用疑態做粒黑色野(人性),再行埋去<br />\n<br />\n黑龍入口:第二個營火部lift中間有得碌出去,有個騎士石像係幻影<br />\n<br />\n黑龍NPC:唔可以去最尾張地圖,同埋要同長樓梯最上面個NPC講左野先<br />\n<br />\n希拉套衫:打完最尾BOSS,係營火向右行行到盡就有NPC殺,殺完就返去長樓梯最上面個位拎,向左行有個環印騎士殺左有圓盤<br />\n<br />\nDS1得PC,PS3,Xbox 360版<br />\nDS2原罪哲人版=連所有DLC+高清些少<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"2cfc00c2d7feea8787eebf7356b22ab2f8174659","tid":204233,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T02:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/